reviewText: If you're remotely planning a trip on an African hunting safari, this book is an absolute must!
great video, very informative helped me greatly on a trip to Africa.
If you are going to hunt African game you owe it to yourself and the game to see this video
DVD had more scratches than expected, but they did not effect the quality. DVD arrived very quickly. This was a highly recommended DVD for an up coming hunt in Africa. DVD explained kill zones well.
